{"tid":2166094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[籃波］林書豪入籍台灣並且已取得護照","createTime":"2020-08-20T08:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T11:26:31.000Z","uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53a285f1d1bd5dc7b98a52fd4b4046436e078148","tid":2166094,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在美國NBA闖出名堂的球員林書豪，在籃球壇的一舉一動，都很受華人注目。現在效力CBA北京首鋼（Beijing Ducks)的他，最近入籍台灣。<br />\n<br />\n林書豪在七月底已經取得台灣護照，一起入籍的還有他的弟弟林書緯。林書豪的爸爸林繼明專程到台灣，感謝相關部門的協助。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的《中央社》報道，林書豪入籍台灣後，可以享受大陸對台26條規定中的優惠，視為是本土球員。若果他繼續留在CBA，所屬的球隊變相可以請多一名外援球員，增強實力。"},{"pid":"81ec277e7920456d186595c3f4d360539366b392","tid":2166094,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"繼續燃燒生命去賺人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b11ec171a4dd47e006b65348efd9579e460d6eb","tid":2166094,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"真係服撚左佢"},{"pid":"255d509320cfe7eb7e3eddc63ef49ee07b36ad47","tid":2166094,"uid":33522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特登入籍台灣黎等隊波可以簽多個外援"},{"pid":"ce43da4affb90045c9dc5da85949dfddfc9daa98","tid":2166094,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"255d509320cfe7eb7e3eddc63ef49ee07b36ad47","tid":2166094,"uid":33522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特登入籍台灣黎等隊波可以簽多個外援"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔拎中華人民共和國護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfdec05bf444d976a7873b1129ff68e44992fb0","tid":2166094,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔拎大陸戶籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" cla